{"tid":1597844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人治港 香港自治","createTime":"2019-09-27T06:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:51:38.000Z","uid":8891,"like":37,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3d81941da36aea10f82f1738be34320253ec91c7","tid":1597844,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"修正部份內容重開這個post:<br />\n<br />\n80年代中英兩方已經明白香港要維持實力，必須要高度自治，國際多國亦多次支持香港自治，我們的盟友美國多次強調中共影響香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n國際開咗張好牌，香港人要識做，新口號要有自治、新文宣要向自己人推廣香港自治重要性。<br />\n<br />\n如果要為今次革命加一句自治新口號，我推介「港人治港，香港自治」<br />\n<br />\n這句口號由「港人治港，高度自治」修改，刪走「高度」，換做「香港」，沒有表示自治程度，即是要100%自治。<br />\n<br />\n港人治港 香港自治"},{"pid":"700c492a113c47cdcca4adc3649b88e1441a3a3b","tid":1597844,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7de1b8702317bc3b499a6b922ba076946595102","tid":1597844,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5add20bfb725ca45c849d973419d615cce5c9914","tid":1597844,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcaba085ff35239f2fbe3441fadba4fa9e859608","tid":1597844,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"香港自治"},{"pid":"f816f89cef99015314bce3152059b1f51fdedd45","tid":1597844,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"777尋日已經話香港無自治<br />\n所以香港人唯有自決"},{"pid":"a12e0b0b96b7b7759fef6cb784bbd0604ddd9473","tid":1597844,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"港人治港 香港自治"},{"pid":"ae500e1cd8315452788413e42a0d9ac9fe80a894","tid":1597844,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a